“Being human is a given, but keeping our humanity is a choice.” 

A powerful quote shared by Saumya, one of our inspiring participants from the #India Hack. 

Saumya believes her country needs a fair education system for all children and young people. Check out her voice note to see what motivated her to make a difference in this space. 

#Goal4 #YOUTHPOWERHACKS @restlessdevelopment
